### 5. Reseting statuses, flushing records and comparison results


```python
comparer.flush_records()
```


```python
comparer.flush_runs()
```


```python
comparer.flush_comparison_scores()
```


```python
comparer.flush_aggregate_scores()
```


```python
comparer.flush_test_statuses()
```
